name: Community Tablet Hospital App
description:
Start of UX/UI project for web with dark theme, strong green contrast and prototyping of options in side blocks.

In the images appear people that are not real https://thispersondoesnotexist.com.

Most of the options are undeveloped so I encourage you to keep creating and modifying everything you think that benefits the user experience.

I hope you can use this sketch in your projects.
